<h2>Options Admin Help</h2>
<h3>Unlimited Product Options!</h3>
<p> The Option architecture is one of the more powerful features of Cartweaver. There can be an unlimited number of options. </p>
<h3>Adding Option Groups </h3>
<p>To add an Option Group you click the Add New link under the Option tab on the Admin menu. This will take you to a simple form that will allow you to add the Option Name.</p>
<h3>Adding Options</h3>
<p>Once you add an option group, click on the group name in the Options tab of the Admin menu to open the Options Administration page. Here you can add and administer options to be listed under this particular option group.</p>
<h3>Administering Options</h3>
<p>Here you can add, edit, delete or archive your Option records. You can also set the order in which you want them to be applied to on the web. If there are products associated with a given option you will not be able to delete the option. You can however Archive the option so it will no longer appear on the web or in the selection fields on the Product Admin page. </p>
